headline: Philip Morris International Stock Surges to New All-Time High. Is It Too Late to Buy the Stock?
summary: Philip Morris International (NYSE: PM) shares hit an all-time high following its latest earnings results.  Philip Morris' biggest growth driver continues to be Zyn.  For those unfamiliar with Zyn, it is a pouch made of nicotine powder and flavoring instead of tobacco, and it has taken the U.S. market by storm.
